data.description: Unique and Private lake house in the city! This one-of-a-kind Bethany Lake craftsman has panoramic water views and an abundance of custom details that make it feel like a secluded retreat. Great room floor plan with primary on the main and gas fireplace, built-ins, gas fireplace and wall of windows framing unobstructed view of Bethany Lake. Kitchen features a large amount of cabinet space, quartz counters, gas range, stainless steal appliances, and eating bar. Dining nook off kitchen with built-in bench seat. Primary ensuite with high ceilings, built-ins, walk-in closet, views and private patio. Primary bath with dual sinks, walk-in shower and heated floor. New roof 2024. Wildlife sightings will be your evening entertainment as you relax on the patio and take in unobstructed sunsets on the lake. This rare find offers relaxation and privacy minutes from the city.
